The paper focuses on improving the user interface design for fallback authentication to encourage users to design stronger answers for security questions. This involves visual feedback to the user based on mnemonics to guide the user to creatively design a stronger answer. This work involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), computer security and cryptography (cs.CR), cyber security (cs.CY), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
